  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the positioning of customized guides designed from
      patients X-Rays (Materialise X-Ray Knee Guides) using computed tomography in primary total
      knee arthroplasty.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
